## Secretary's report

Jonathan reported he'd taken a brief look at moving the website to
ikiwiki while at DebConf, but failed to easily export the current content
from Plone to enable this. This spurred a little discussion about other
options, including Joshua suggesting he might find time to look at
Drupal.

