## Any other business

The Debian Project Leader had asked about the possibility of "sustaining
membership", involving being able to make regular donations. Michael stated
that our payment processors already allowed us to take recurrent charges
and suggested we might want some sort of status badge or other
acknowledgement.

debian.eu was also brought up, and Jonathan agreed to take a look at
drafting an initial letter to the current owner.

